# Teacher Job Satisfaction Analysis

## 📌 Project Overview
This project analyzes teacher job satisfaction using Machine Learning techniques.

## 🎯 Objective
To predict whether a teacher is satisfied or not based on factors like workload, environment, and work-life balance.

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
- Google Colab

## 🤖 Model Used
- Random Forest Classifier

## 📊 Results
The model achieved good accuracy and showed that job satisfaction depends on multiple nonlinear factors.

## 💼 Business Impact
- Helps schools improve teacher retention
- Reduces burnout
- Supports better work-life balance

## 🚀 Future Scope
- Use larger dataset
- Try advanced models
- Deploy as web app
